        <!-- <m>1</m>\amp <m>  \</m>1\left(1+\frac{0.05}{2}\right)+\<m>1\left(1+\frac{0.05}{2}\right)\left(\frac{0.05}{2}\right)</m>\bigstrut \\ -->
        <!-- \amp \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ -->
        <!-- =<m>\</m>1\left(1+\frac{0.05}{2}\right)^2=\<m>1.050625</m>\bigstrut \\\hline -->
        <!-- \end{tabular} -->
        <!-- \end{center} -->

       The effective yield in this case is approximately <m>5.06%</m>.
      </p>
