            How good was your guess in <xref ref="DRILLBacteriaGuess1"></xref>?
            Whether it was good or bad isn<rsq/>t really the point. Either way take
            a moment to hone your guessing skills by considering why you
            guessed the way you did. What was your intuition telling you about
            the problem?
          </p>
        </statement>
      </exercise>
      <p>
        A natural question to ask is, <q>How long will it take for the culture
        to reach <m>4</m> grams?</q>  Translating this into a mathematical question,
