    <p>
Show that <m> \cosh(it)=\frac{e^{it}+e^{-it}}{2}=\cos(t)</m>
</p>
</statement>
</task>
<task>
  <statement>
    <p>
      Show that
      <m>\frac{1}{i}\sinh(it)=\frac{e^{it}-e^{-it}}{2i}=\sin(t)</m>.
</p>
</statement>
</task>
</problem>
